{%- style -%}
  .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
    padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    }
  }
{%- endstyle -%}

<section class="pl-faq section-{{ section.id }}-padding" id="faq" aria-labelledby="pl-faq-heading">
  <div class="pl-faq__container page-width">
    <div class="pl-faq__header">
      <p class="pl-faq__eyebrow">A few useful answers</p>
      <h2 id="pl-faq-heading" class="pl-faq__heading">Before you order</h2>
      <p class="pl-faq__subtitle">Short answers on sourcing, freshness, delivery, and storage.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pl-faq__list">
      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>Where do PureLeven spices come from?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p>Most of our core spices come from the <strong>Idukki side of Kerala</strong>, including Rajakumari. That cooler hill climate helps pepper, cardamom, and cloves hold fuller aroma and flavor.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>How do you keep them fresh?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p>We favor whole spices, smaller packing cycles, and a shorter route from source to kitchen. That helps keep natural oils and aroma intact. We do not add artificial colors, fillers, or preservatives.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>How fast do you deliver?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p>Most orders across India arrive in <strong>4 to 5 working days</strong>. Orders above <strong>&#8377;649</strong> ship free. If you need help, you can track the order from your confirmation email or message us on <a href="https://wa.me/918848265849" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>Why do you sell 8mm cardamom?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p><strong>8mm pods</strong> are larger, usually carry fuller seeds, and give a stronger aroma in chai, sweets, and everyday cooking. Smaller 7mm pods are more common in the retail market.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>How should I store whole spices?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p>Keep them in an <strong>airtight jar</strong> away from heat, steam, and direct light. A cool kitchen cabinet works well. Whole spices stay fresher longer when they are not stored near the stove.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="pl-faq__item">
        <summary class="pl-faq__question">
          <span>What if there is a problem with my order?</span>
          <svg class="pl-faq__chevron" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="pl-faq__answer">
          <p>If something arrives damaged or incorrect, contact us within <strong>7 days</strong> on <a href="https://wa.me/918848265849" rel="noopener">WhatsApp (+91 88482 65849)</a> or email at <a href="mailto:purelevenexim@gmail.com">purelevenexim@gmail.com</a>. We will sort out a replacement or refund.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

